ady | |- | 1949 | ''[[Tarzan's Magic Fountain]]'' | Mr. Trask | |- | 1949 | ''[[Bride of Vengeance]]'' | Vanetti | |- | 1949 | ''[[Search for Danger]]'' | Kirk | |- | 1950 | ''[[The Kid from Texas]]'' | Alexander Kain | |- | 1950 | ''[[Destination Murder]]'' | Armitage | |- | 1950 | ''[[The Furies (1950 film)|The Furies]]'' | Mr. Reynolds | |- | 1951 | ''[[As Young as You Feel]]'' | Louis McKinley | |- | 1952 | ''[[Wait Till the Sun Shines, Nellie (film)|Wait Till the Sun Shines, Nellie]]'' | Lloyd Slocum | |- | 1954 | ''[[The Silver Chalice (film)|The Silver Chalice]]'' | Kester | |- | 1955 | ''[[East of Eden (film)|East of Eden]]'' | Will Hamilton | with James Dean |- | 1955 | ''[[Kiss Me Deadly]]'' | Dr. G.E. Soberin | |- | 1955 | ''[[Illegal (1955 film)|Illegal]]'' | Frank Garland | |- | 1957 | ''[[She Devil (1957 film)|She Devil]]'' | Dr. Richard Bach | |- | 1958 | ''[[Machete (1958 film)|Machete]]'' | Don Luis Montoya | |- | 1959 |''[[The Sound and the Fury (1959 film)|The Sound and the Fury]]'' | Earl Snopes | |- | 1959 | ''[[These Thousand Hills]]'' | Marshal Conrad | |- | 1959 | ''[[Middle of the Night]]'' | Walter Lockman | with Fredric March and Kim Novak |- | 1959 |''[[The Wonderful Country]]'' | Texas Ranger Capt. Rucker | |- | 1959 | ''[[Suddenly, Last Summer (film)|Suddenly, Last Summer]]'' | Dr. Lawrence J. Hockstader | |- | 1965 | ''Once Upon a Tractor'' | Colonel | Short |- | 1966 | ''[[Gamera:_The_Giant_Monster#English_versions|Gammera: The Invincible]]'' | Secretary of Defense | |- | 1967 | ''[[Come Spy with Me (film)|Come Spy with Me]]'' | Walter Ludeker | |- | 1969 | ''[[The Wild Bunch]]'' | Pat Harrigan | (final film role) |}
