'''Shoaib Aamer''' (born 3 January 1968) is a Pakistani former [[cricket]]er. He played four [[first-class cricket|first-class]] and five [[List A cricket|List A]] matches for several domestic teams in Pakistan between 1991 and 1995.<ref name="Bio">{{Cite web|url=http://www.espncricinfo.com/ci/content/player/42847.html |title=Shoaib Aamer |accessdate=24 October 2016 |work=[[ESPN Cricinfo]]}}</ref><ref name="CA">{{Cite web|url=https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Players/19/19766/19766.html |title=Shoaib Aamer |accessdate=24 October 2016 |work=Cricket Archive}}</ref>
