{{Uniform hyperbolic tiles db|Uniform hyperbolic tiling stat table|U65_s}} In [[geometry]], the '''snub pentahexagonal tiling''' is a [[Uniform tilings in hyperbolic plane|uniform]] tiling of the [[Hyperbolic geometry|hyperbolic plane]]. It has [[Schläfli symbol]] of sr{6,5}.
